scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Each box contains a full academic year of course files labeled with the term and year, course number, and instructor name. Within each box, folders are arranged in alpha order by residential college sponsorship (indicated by the inclusion of the college's initials in the course number, e.g. CSBK stands for College Seminar Berkeley). Folders for fall term precede those of spring, but are found in the same college section. Each folder contains a complete course proposal, instructor appointment form, copy of the I-9, and student evaluations (two kinds -- the program form and the Registrar's on line evaluations). Multiple pocket files for any instructor are grouped together with the most recent term in front (this is because previous student evaluations are reviewed when reconsidering a course for approval).
